snippet.title: Auto Chess Legends - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Download now: https://autochess.page.link/dl
Auto Chess Legends is a strategy game mixed with chess, that emphasises fast and fluid gameplay: Auto fight across an 8x8 field chessboard using your idle heroes as your autobattler game pieces.
How you play your pieces matters, far more than how fast you can tap!
